What you need to know:

Ocholla said the decision had been taken for the good and well-being of members of the respective clubs in those countiesMeanwhile Kenya’s most popular inter-club foursomes golf tournament, the Tannahill golf tournament also known as the “Easter Weekend golf tournament’’ usually held over the Easter weekend, will now take place from August 6This is the first time in over 90 years that the Tannahill Shield will be held outside the Easter weekend